title: cUNI Uniswap Proposal 4 Vote
body:
https://app.uniswap.org/#/vote/4

This vote acts as a signal for the voting of the Compound community multisig vote which controls a delegation of 11.7M UNI for this proposal. The multisig will only vote if a 10% quorum of eligible cUNI votes are cast.

This vote ends earlier than the Uniswap proposal to allow time for the community multisig to convene and vote.
author: 0x2B384212EDc04Ae8bB41738D05BA20E33277bf33
